    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なら……私が今回は優を助ける\n優が生徒会長になれるように、私も手伝うわ",
      "startTime": 5.5593206175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？\nで、でも瑠依ちゃんはうちが生徒会長になるんは……",
      "startTime": 10.4392749786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、正直に言えば、あまり納得はしていないわ\nトリエルの――三人の時間が減るのは、嫌だもの",
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これまで優は私がやりたいことを、支えてくれた\n私も……そしてすみれも、優に助けられてきた",
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "だから今度は、優のことを手伝いたいし、支えたいの\n今回は、私が優の助けになるわ",
      "startTime": 38.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……うち、絶対生徒会長になってみせる\nアイドル活動もちゃんとやります！",
      "startTime": 47.1608170826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、そうね……実は……まだちょっと、気持ちは……\n応援しきれていないんだけど……",
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "漫画に影響を受けたからって、運命だなんて……\nもし生徒会長になって、アイドル活動が疎かになったら",
      "startTime": 63.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、ダメよ瑠依！\n私は優を手伝う、支えるって決めたんだもの！",
      "startTime": 70.2531534899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、何やら複雑そうやなぁ……\nあんな、瑠依ちゃん、聞いて",
      "startTime": 78.6207356434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちが生徒会長を目指すのは\n『ここまま』もきっかけの一つではあるんやけど……",
      "startTime": 84.1238334019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "この学校を、もっと良くしたいって想いはあるんよ\n……まだちゃんと、考えはまとまってへんけど",
      "startTime": 91.8238334019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのね……なら、いつかその考えがまとまったら\n私にも教えて。私ももう迷わない。全力で応援するわ",
      "startTime": 100.1653732806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、瑠依ちゃんが応援してくれるなら\nこの選挙、なおさら負けられへんわ！",
      "startTime": 109.5823366164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、生徒会長選挙、必ず勝ちにいきましょう！\n一年生生徒会長、鈴村優を目指して！",
      "startTime": 117.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、ほんまにええ子やわぁ\nしっかりしてるし、頼りになるし",
      "startTime": 127.4380293527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "「ライブの準備は私に任せて、選挙頑張ってね！」\nなんて言われたら、より一層気合いも入るわ",
      "startTime": 134.7046960193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、私達、すみれに助けられることも多いわね\nでも……無理しないかちょっと心配だわ",
      "startTime": 143.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そうやね、そこはうちらも気を付けとこか\nすみれちゃんは頑張り過ぎるとこ、あるしな",
      "startTime": 152.1294810611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "なら、私が気を付けておくわ\n優は心置きなく選挙に集中してちょうだい",
      "startTime": 158.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんも、ほんまにありがとう\nうち、凄く心強いわ",
      "startTime": 165.3046059924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ところでな、実は今悩んでることがあって……\nちょっと相談に乗ってほしいんやけど",
      "startTime": 172.9046059924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "……うち、生徒会長選の公約に迷っててな\nここ何日か、学校でいろんな人に質問したんや",
      "startTime": 180.0379393258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらこの学校が、もっと良くなると思います？\nなんでも聞かせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 190.537940343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "学食のメニューにもっとボリュームがほしい……\nふむふむ、逆にハーフサイズも選べたらええかもなぁ",
      "startTime": 197.0841879359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "図書館にもっと漫画がほしい……\nそれはうちも思ってました！　置いてほしいなぁ！",
      "startTime": 207.7712909697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_13_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "視聴覚室で映画が観たい？　分かるわ～！\nうちもあの大画面で映画やアニメ、観たいです！",
      "startTime": 219.9712909697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
